00:00:00.710 --> 00:00:02.251
LAUREN STOVALL: |
always wanted a dog

00:00:02.251 --> 00:00:03.850
that I could have off leash.

00:00:03.850 --> 00:00:05.820
He sticks with me on
hikes, if I tell him to.

00:00:10.590 --> 00:00:12.280
My name is Lauren Stovall.

00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:15.060
I an a Bluegrass musician.

00:00:15.060 --> 00:00:17.110
[MUSIC PLAYING] Spreads
